  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this of study is to identify the incidence of mechanical failures after spinal&#xD;
      fusion within one year of surgery and to assess the related risk factors.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Not yet recruiting</overall_status>
